          "The Chevy 3100s have caught the eye of collectors who want a utilitarian classic. We’d say they stick it in their garage, but this might not fit in yours. Anyway, the look of this truck is definitely vintage with those prominent fenders, smaller windows, and that iconic alligator hood."
